The colon-based syntax was voted down.<p>What went live in 5.4 was support for brackets in lieu of array()<p><pre><code>    // Typical array syntax
    $arr = array(&#x27;key&#x27; => &#x27;asdf&#x27;);

    // Supported in 5.4+
    $arr = [&#x27;key&#x27; => &#x27;asdf&#x27;];</code></pre>
